891
01:34:13,767 --> 01:34:14,897
She has no family.

892
01:34:14,902 --> 01:34:17,769
She has no friends.

893
01:34:17,838 --> 01:34:20,306
You're her only contact.

894
01:34:20,374 --> 01:34:23,639
And I'm told you
don't visit her.

895
01:34:23,711 --> 01:34:25,508
No, I don't.

896
01:34:25,513 --> 01:34:27,879
When she gets out,
